Home to Armin's productions and a platform for new and exciting talent to release their tunes. Armind, one of the most beloved sub-labels of Armada Music, isn't only known for its beautiful little angel, but also for serving quality beats, mind-dazzling melodies and haunting vocals. Armind looks back upon a very special year with outstanding productions. And a selection of 10 of these, can be found on the 'Armind - Best of 2013' pack! Enjoy this year's overview of Armind Recordings, with tunes by Armin van Buuren, Omnia, Bobina, Orjan Nilsen, Andrew Rayel and more!
